==NFL draft==
{{main|2018 NFL draft}}

There were a total of 45 athletes from the Atlantic Coast Conference selected in the 2018 NFL Draft.  This was the second most from a single conference in the draft, and the third most from the ACC all–time.  Georgia Tech was the only member university to not have a player drafted.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theacc.com/news/2018/4/28/football-acc-has-45-selected-in-2018-nfl-draft.aspx|title=ACC Has 45 Selected in 2018 NFL Draft|publisher=Atlantic Coast Conference|website=theacc.com|date=April 28, 2018|access-date=April 30, 2018}}</ref>

